Follow the below steps to compile and run the cleint and server

1:Save the client and server at two different locations
For Server
2: Change the directory on terminal and execute make -f tcpforkedserver to compile the server program
3: Execute./tcp_forked_server to run the server
For Client
4: Change the directory on a new terminal to client directory and execute make -f tcpclient to compile the client
5: Execute ./tcp_client 127.0.0.1 Doc 10003 to run the client -arguments are the server ip, File name to be copied and the port number 
6: Verify the file has been copied from the server location to client location.
